                "invention-title": [
                    "Silicon material alkali wash additive and application thereof",
                    "一种硅料碱洗添加剂及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of silicon photovoltaics, and particularly relates to a silicon material alkali wash additive and application thereof. The silicon material alkali wash additive can strengthen the cleaning of grease impurities such as fingerprints and the like, and achieves the purposes of reducing silicon material loss, reducing the use amount of hydrogen peroxide, reducing the silicon material loss and improving the silicon material recovery rate. By adding the wetting agent with the molecular structure containing any one of hydroxyl groups or carboxyl groups and at least one of phenolic hydroxyl groups and acylamino groups, the wetting effect of the aqueous alkali on the surface of the silicon material is effectively improved, and the effect of rapidly cleaning the seriously dirty positions such as fingerprints can be further achieved. Meanwhile, the oxidation resistance of the silicon material is effectively improved, so that the silicon material is prevented from being excessively oxidized and damaged in the alkali washing process. The oxidizing agent and hydrogen peroxide are combined for use, so that the oxidation effect on organic substances in cutting fluid and fingerprints can be improved. Meanwhile, the actual dosage of hydrogen peroxide is effectively reduced, and the production cost is further reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于硅光伏技术领域，具体涉及一种硅料碱洗添加剂及其应用。本发明的硅料碱洗添加剂可强化对指纹印等油脂类杂质的清洗，达到降低硅料损耗并实现双氧水用量降低，降低硅料损耗，提高硅料回收率的目的。通过添加分子结构中含有羟基或羧基基团中的任意一种，还包括酚羟基、酰胺基基团中的至少一种的润湿剂，有效提升碱溶液在硅料表面的润湿效果，进一步促使指纹印等脏污严重的位置也能达到快速清洗的效果。同时有效提升其抗氧化性，从而防止硅料在碱洗过程中发生过度氧化损伤。本发明的氧化剂和双氧水结合使用，有助于提升其对切割液和指纹印中有机物质的氧化效果。同时有效降低双氧水的实际用量，进一步促使生产成本降低。"
                }
